skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dullsville d. j.
des: Dullsville DJ is adapted from the celebrity David Jackson, an amateur comedian who has coined some of the nations most ridiculous terms. Ask for a useless Dullsville DJ fact, or ask Alexa to tell you what Dullsville DJ thinks about drivers and maybe you will learn a new word to shout when someone cuts you off.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
